title: Ron Carter Discusses His Bass Tone and Playing Style
fulltitle: Ron Carter Discusses His Bass Tone and Playing Style
description: In this clip from www.artistshousemusic.org - Jazz legend Ron Carter discusses how he developed his remarkably rich tone on the upright bass, and shares his thoughts on how jazz musicians communicate to listeners.
